t aired on December 5, 2015.\n\n{{As of|2020|04|11|df=US}}, '''225'''episodes of ''Knowing Bros'' have been aired.\n\n==Series overview==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n! style=\"padding: 0 16px;\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"| Year\n! style=\"padding: 0 8px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Episodes\n! colspan=\"2\"| Originally aired\n|-\n! style=\"padding: 0 12px;\"| First aired\n! Last aired\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FA5858; height:10px;\"|\n| [[#2015|2015]]\n| 4\n| {{Start date|December 5, 2015}}\n| {{End date|December 26, 2015}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#FE642E; height:10px;\"|\n| [[#2016|2016]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|January 2, 2016}}\n| {{End date|December 24, 2016}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#F7BE81; height:10px;\"|\n| [[#2017|2017]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|January 7, 2017}}\n| {{End date|December 30, 2017}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#F7D358; height:10px;\"|\n| [[#2018|2018]]\n| 52\n| {{Start date|January 6, 2018}}\n| {{End date|December 29, 2018}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#F2F5A9; height:10px;\"|\n| [[#2019|2019]]\n| 51\n| {{Start date|January 5, 2019}}\n| {{End date|December 28, 2019}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#D8F781; height:10px;\"|\n| [[#2020|2020]]\n| {{TBA}}\n| {{Start date|January 4, 2020}}\n| {{TBA}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Episodes==\nIn the table below, <span style=\"color:blue\">'''the blue numbers'''</span> represent the lowest ratings and <span style=\"color:red\">'''the red numbers'''</span> represent the highest ratings.\n\n===2015===\n{{hidden begin\n|title = List of episodes in 2015 (episode 1\u20134)\n|titlestyle = background:#FA5858; text-align:center;\n}}\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style = \"font-size: 90%;\"\n|-\n!width=35|Ep. #\n!width=130|Air Date\n!width=500|Guest(s)\n!width=600|Remarks\n!width=100|AGB Nielsen Ratings<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nielsenkorea.co.kr/tv_terrestrial_day.asp?menu=Tit_1&sub_menu=2_1&area=00|title=AGB Daily Ratings: this links to current day-select the date from drop down menu|website=AGB Niels