{"title_page": "Shepherd of Fire", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Shepherd of Fire\n| cover      = Shepherd of fire A7.jpeg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Avenged Sevenfold]]\n| album      = [[Hail to the King (Avenged Sevenfold album)|Hail to the King]]\n| released   = November 7, 2013\n| format     =\n| recorded   =\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = [[Heavy metal music|Heavy metal]]\n| length     = 5:25\n| label      = [[Warner Bros. Records|Warner Bros.]]\n| writer     =\n* [[M. Shadows]]\n* [[Synyster Gates]]\n* [[Zacky Vengeance]]\n* [[Johnny Christ]]\n| producer   = [[Mike Elizondo]]\n| prev_title = [[Hail to the King (song)|Hail to the King]]\n| prev_year  = 2013\n| next_title = [[The Stage (Avenged Sevenfold song)|The Stage]]\n| next_year  = 2016\n}}\n\n\"'''Shepherd of Fire'''\" is the second single from ''[[Hail to the King (Avenged Sevenfold album)|Hail to the King]]'', the sixth studio album from American [[heavy metal music|heavy metal]] band [[Avenged Sevenfold]].  Released on November 7, 2013, the song was a No.1 single on [[Mainstream Rock (chart)|Mainstream Rock]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/280315/avenged-sevenfold/chart?f=376 |title=Avenged Sevenfold - Chart history |publisher=Billboard |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23}}</ref> and is the theme song of the ''[[Call of Duty: Black Ops II]]'' Zombies map \"Origins\", included in the final [[downloadable content]] compilation named ''Apocalypse''.<ref>{{cite web|title=AVENGED SEVENFOLD: Trailer For 'Hail To The King' Animated Series|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/avenged-sevenfold-trailer-for-hail-to-the-king-animated-series/|publisher=BlabberMouth}}</ref> It is also featured in the mixed-martial arts video game ''[[EA Sports UFC]]''.\n\n==Personnel==\n;Avenged Sevenfold\n* [[M. Shadows]] \u2013 [[vocals]]\n* [[Zacky Vengeance]] \u2013 [[rhythm guitar]], backing vocals\n* [[Synyster Gates]] \u2013 lead guitar, backing voca