k]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/280315/avenged-sevenfold/chart?f=376 |title=Avenged Sevenfold - Chart history |publisher=Billboard |date= |accessdate=2014-08-23}}</ref> and is the theme song of the ''[[Call of Duty: Black Ops II]]'' Zombies map \"Origins\", included in the final [[downloadable content]] compilation named ''Apocalypse''.<ref>{{cite web|title=AVENGED SEVENFOLD: Trailer For 'Hail To The King' Animated Series|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/avenged-sevenfold-trailer-for-hail-to-the-king-animated-series/|publisher=BlabberMouth}}</ref> It is also featured in the mixed-martial arts video game ''[[EA Sports UFC]]''.\n\n==Personnel==\n;Avenged Sevenfold\n* [[M. Shadows]] \u2013 [[vocals]]\n* [[Zacky Vengeance]] \u2013 [[rhythm guitar]], backing vocals\n* [[Synyster Gates]] \u2013 lead guitar, backing vocals\n* [[Johnny Christ]] \u2013 bass guitar, backing vocals\n* [[Arin Ilejay]] \u2013 [[drums]]\n;Session musicians\n\n* [[Mike Elizondo]], Brent Arrowood \u2013 Sound fx\n* [[David Campbell (composer)|David Campbell]] \u2013 Orchestra arranger & conductor\n* Suzie Katayama \u2013 [[cello]]\n* Ed Meares \u2013 [[upright bass]]\n* Joe Meyer, John Reynolds \u2013 [[french horn]]\n* [[John Fumo]], Rick Baptist \u2013 [[trumpet]]\n* Alan Kaplan \u2013 [[trombone]] \n* Steven Holtman, Andrew Martin \u2013 [[bass trombone]]\n* Douglas Tornquist \u2013 [[tuba]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/hail-to-the-king-mw0002561282/credits |title=Hail to the King - Avenged Sevenfold &#124; Credits |publisher=AllMusic |date=2013-08-26 |accessdate=2014-08-23}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Chart (2013\u201314)\n! Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardcanadarock|31|artist=Avenged Sevenfold|accessdate=June 28, 2013|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|UKrock|12|date=2013-09-07|accessdate=June 28, 2013|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechar